==¿Cómo puedo comprar vehículos de carretera?==
# Para construir un [[es/Manual/Vehículos de carretera|vehículo de carretera]], [[es/Manual/Construir depósitos de vehículos de carretera|construya un depósito]] y luego haga clic en él.
# Aparecerá la ventana depósito de vehículos. Seleccione el botón "Nuevos vehículos" y una nueva ventana aparecerá con una lista de los vehículos disponibles.<br/>[[File:es/Manual/Tutorial bus 5.png|frame|none|Dentro del depósito...]]
# Seleccione uno y haga clic en "Comprar vehículo" en la parte inferior de esta ventana.
# El vehículo aparecerá en la ventana del depósito y se abrirá la ventana de control del vehículo.
# Dele [[es/Manual/Órdenes|órdenes]] o [[es/Manual/Reformar vehículos|reforme el vehículo]] en su caso, a continuación, ¡haga clic en el botón rojo "parado" para poner en marcha el vehículo!<br/>[[File:es/Manual/Stopped bus.png|frame|none|Dentro del depósito...]]

==Dar órdenes a su vehículo de carretera==
{{es/Pendiente de traducción}}

#In the vehicle window, click the ''Orders'' button [[File:en/Manual/Orders.png]]. 
#Click the ''Go To'' button, and then click on your first bus station with the special go to cursor. This will add an instruction to the vehicle's orders; ''Go to <station name>''. 
#Click ''Go To'' again, and add your second station to the vehicles order list in the same way. Once a vehicle has reached the end of its instructions, it will start over from the beginning.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Tutorial bus 6.png|frame|none|Giving orders]]
#In the vehicle window, press the ''status bar'' at the bottom that says ''Stopped'', and your bus will leave the depot and start driving between the stations.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Tutorial bus 7.png|frame|none|Your first bus is about to arrive at the bus station.]]

==How do I sell / delete road vehicles?==
There are a few ways to sell a road vehicle. You can sell one vehicle at a time, or sell all vehicles in a certain depot. Either way, the vehicles you want to sell need to be stopped inside the depot, so you need to send the vehicle to the depot first.

# Click on a road vehicle to open it's ''vehicle window''.
# Click the ''Send vehicle to depot'' button at the right side of the window.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Buying-road-vehicles-6.png|none|frame|Click on the road depot-like botton to send a road to the nearest depot.]]
# Now wait until the road vehicle has arrived at the road depot. In the meantime, you can close the road's vehicle window; you won't be needing that any more!
# As soon as the road vehicle has arrived at the road depot, click on this depot to open the ''Road Depot'' window. You now should be able to find the road vehicle in the depot's window.
# One way to sell the road vehicle is to drag it to the sell-vehicle-icon:<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Buying-road-vehicles-7.png|none|frame|Drag a road vehicle to the first of the three buttons at the right to sell it.]]
# Another way to sell a road vehicle is to click on the ''Sell all vehicles'' button: . Please note that this will sell all vehicles stopped inside the depot.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Buying-road-vehicles-8.png|none|frame|Click on the second button to sell all road vehicles which are stopped inside the depot. You'll be presented with a confirmation window asking if you're certain about what you're about to do.]]

